    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required Gradation 2 level for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to Gradation 1 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4 allowances for MRL 2. GCI of 3.2% confirms adequate mesh convergence. NIH predictions within combined uncertainty bounds across all 5 operating points. RH < 1 acceptance criterion satisfied. Overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support regulatory submission for Class II CPB device.",
